snippet.title: PLOT! - Solo developed, 3D Indie Arcade Platformer now available on Steam
snippet.description:
"It's Alive!" Yup - Finally, PLOT! is finished and available now on the Steam Store:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2761780/PLOT/

It's currently on sale (first week), and if you're still not convinced there is a FREE DEMO that can be downloaded at the above link.
GLHF!
